solution.cpp: In member function __helper__
Line 29: Char 25: error: 'Solution' was not declared in this scope
       vector<int> ret = Solution().twoSum(param_1, param_2); return ret;
                         ^~~~~~~~


样例输入：


[2,7,11,15]
9



