&lt;p&gt;I am not sure if this is what you need, but you can take a look at this one &lt;a href="https://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;goreleaser&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
